data.description: Presenting the home you've been eagerly anticipating! This impeccable residence boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, along with an office space, and brand new HVAC unit as of June 2023, all nestled on a .52-acre lot in the desirable Pershing Hills neighborhood. Upon entry, be captivated by the beautiful wainscoting detail in the main floor entryway and dining room. Throughout the main floor, revel in the allure of stunning wood floors, adorning the expansive great room and well-appointed kitchen. The kitchen boasts an eat-in area, pantry, granite countertops, and stainless-steel appliances, catering to both style and functionality. Ascend to the upper level to discover a vast owner's suite, complete with a generously sized private bath, his & her vanity, and a spacious walk-in closet.
